{"tid":1447894,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"咩叫和理非？？","createTime":"2019-08-11T16:16:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T16:44:14.000Z","uid":195727,"like":29,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"a8f48fd6ea444856871a5abdb7d553d8f5227fce","tid":1447894,"uid":195727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:16:27.000Z","msg":"唔計之前 <br />\n只講最近<br />\n有個女仔比人非禮<br />\n有個女仔比人射爆眼<br />\n有個男仔比人剪斷手腳筋<br />\n有黑警室內放煙<br />\n等等<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我真係屌你老母仲同我講和平理性非暴力</span></span><br />\n<br />\n以後<br />\n如果你唔係行動不便<br />\n一係就勇武 一係就被勇武<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">勇武</span></span><br />\n主動出擊<br />\n<br />\n過唔到自己心理關口<br />\n唔緊要<br />\n做<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">被勇武</span></span><br />\n係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>可行</strong></span>嘅情況下負責救手足（如今日果個：撞低黑警比自己友走），支援，call 律師。冇事發生就負責叫口號打氣。<br />\n<br />\n成日做和理非 俾人打俾人捉就走 點贏<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">救到就救 勸到就勸 顧掂自己 再救手足<br />\n人數同決心係我地嘅優勢</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\nFight for future together"},{"pid":"a90d546c89dd93f5aea2f73580a3ad3edfd471a7","tid":1447894,"uid":195727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:16:38.000Z","msg":"黑警死全家"},{"pid":"0da3531d44b9c59147293bdc53b7b4de7fd03236","tid":1447894,"uid":195727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:16:50.000Z","msg":"黑警死全家"},{"pid":"c05fc224e081e56512b8c6895dfa36ce3fb1962e","tid":1447894,"uid":195727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:17:01.000Z","msg":"黑警死全家"},{"pid":"ff3034c5205a2a63e1e025b965e254ec2d626af8","tid":1447894,"uid":195727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:17:47.000Z","msg":"黑警死全家"},{"pid":"818ef1000bc6a085fbdcf829b3aa164c544679f1","tid":1447894,"uid":247614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:17:52.000Z","msg":"無論你覺得應該點 行動之前請注意<br />\n<br />\n[戰術] 行動生存指南 - 示威守則及警察策略<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1395112\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1395112</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">三軍可以奪帥 匹夫不可奪志</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"b7b65183b25791335e6eb67a7a2e4d7e645cadd3","tid":1447894,"uid":171395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:17:54.000Z","msg":"唔該你出一份力，肯出post，聽日就係人都知入機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n標題：「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場<br />\n<br />\n無時間文宣<br />\n見POST者，自行Copy開新Post，要連登全部都係呢個Post<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n812起 1PM，有人性既你立刻罷工，百萬人進入機場，咩都唔做，勢要討回雙眼<br />\n機場因為100萬人係機場而暫停運作，不是們的責任，是因為機場不夠大<br />\n圍到出青馬，都全條橋唔夠闊<br />\n<br />\n統一口號，兩句，要入健力士，等歷史知道<br />\n「黑警還眼」<br />\n「五大訴求，缺一不可」<br />\n<br />\n黑警聽住：<br />\n一係你就入機場殺哂所有人<br />\n一係你就還返隻眼出黎<br />\n否則百萬人不離開機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大群：<a href=\"https://t.me/airport730\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fairport730&d=6RyWY35l7oH3ui7gcEo%2FTGCvuqnjOb%2FiGpmC2gL%2Fng4%3D&h=dcfdf11b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/airport730</a><br />\n實時Channel: <a href=\"https://t.me/hk730air\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhk730air&d=6RyWY35l7oH3ui7gcEo%2FTGCvuqnjOb%2FiGpmC2gL%2Fng4%3D&h=07c61c56\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hk730air</a>"},{"pid":"0cb075f03c71025102ec92b88becb34adcbee51c","tid":1447894,"uid":195727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:17:57.000Z","msg":"黑警死全家"},{"pid":"2bb694dd1a6848d7f1183194ae7f3272fc7d48b7","tid":1447894,"uid":199816,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:18:06.000Z","msg":"集體PM民陣發起大遊行<br />\n<br />\n和理非大遊行<br />\n<br />\n(幫下手散出去👆🏿)"},{"pid":"e435b923561aaecbc47c3f4d32a22630cb29db46","tid":1447894,"uid":195727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T1